<HEADLINE> Development Bank Expanding International Business </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 6 (Xinhua) -- The State Development Bank (SDB),
one of the three policy-oriented banks in China, has raised 3.4
billion US dollars in overseas funds for key projects, including
the Three Gorges Project and the expansion of Qinshan Nuclear
Power Plant.
</P>
