earned 10 million dollars in profits last year.
</P>
<P>
At the beginning of the year, the bank issued 330 million
dollars in Yankee bonds in the U.S. It issued 30 billion yen in
Samurai bonds in Japan early last year. It is doing business with
many foreign banks and financial institutions. 
