Alternate Executive Director Godfrey Goseb in Freetown last week.
</P>
<P>
Democracy has brought "great expectations" to Sierra Leoneans
only "in terms of an improvement in their living standards," he
noted.
</P>
<P>
"The government will therefore not introduce any measure that
will lead to explosive situations," he added.
</P>
<P>
