<HEADLINE> French President to Visit Brazil </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, March 5 (Xinhua) -- French President Jacques Chirac
will visit Brazil between March 11 and 13, government sources
said today.
</P>
<P>
