relations with Brazil since Brazilian President Fernando Henrique
Cardoso visited France in May 1996.
</P>
<P>
The French president will continue his Latin American trip to
Uruguay, Paraguay, Argentina and Bolivia, member countries of the
Southern Common Market, an economic bloc that represents one of
the French government's current priorities. 
